8	//
9	// The macro expands to a statement that streams into a temporary; the
10	// message is fully built with operator<< before being flushed as one line,
11	// so multi-threaded logging doesn't interleave partial lines (each line is
12	// written with a single fwrite-backed ostream::flush at the end).
